3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): Feature learning is also an important component of artificial intelligence, and the proposed algorithm can be used for data pre-processing in various AI applications. 
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper proposes an iterative algorithm to optimize the objective function, which involves solving a low-rank regression problem and a sparse optimization problem. 
5. cs.ST (Statistics): The paper discusses the interpretation of the results of PCA and proposes a new objective function that assigns an optimal weight to each feature, which can be viewed as a statistical analysis of the data.
